snippet.title: Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom - Official Gameplay Trailer | The Mix Showcase March 2023
snippet.description: Check out gameplay, various levels, and more in this latest trailer for Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom. Zip along in this arcade bump'a'jump platformer game where you take people for rides and the oil industry for all they have. Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom is headed to PC via Steam.
